<h3>Conjugation Quick Reference</h3>

<p>This is a quick reference for conjugating regular Italian verbs. Endings are shown for each verb type and tense/mood, with examples.</p>

<h4>Legend</h4>
<ul class="mb-4">
    <li><strong>io</strong> = I</li>
    <li><strong>tu</strong> = you (singular informal)</li>
    <li><strong>lui/lei</strong> = he/she</li>
    <li><strong>noi</strong> = we</li>
    <li><strong>voi</strong> = you (plural)</li>
    <li><strong>loro</strong> = they</li>
</ul>

